<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>lex-au — Commonwealth Acts as AKN XML</title></head>
<body>
<h1>lex-au</h1>
<p>Browse the lex-au corpus — Commonwealth Acts in force, rendered from AKN 3.0 XML. Each Act page links to its raw XML source. Full dataset: <a href="https://github.com/cchew/lex-au">GitHub</a> / <a href="https://huggingface.co/datasets/cchew/lex-au">Hugging Face</a>.</p>
<ul>
{% for act in acts %}
  <li><a href="{{ act.site_path }}">{{ act.name }}</a> ({{ act.effective_date }})</li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
</body>
</html>
